<abstract><t>This document describes how EVPN can be used to offer a multi-homed L3VPN service leveraging EVPN Layer 2 access redundancy. The solution offers single IP peering to the Customer Edge (CE) nodes, rapid failure detection, minimal fail-over time and make-before-break paradigm for maintenance.</t></abstract>

